8E%D8%B3%D9%8E%D8%AD%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be spacious"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make room for"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to clear (the space), to expand","examples":[{"text":"بعد أن وافق المريض الروسي فاليري سبيريدونوف على التطوّع لإجراء العملية، واستبدال جسده المصاب بمرض ضمور العضلات والأعصاب، بجسد إنسان سليم ولكن ميت دماغياً، فإنه اعتذر أخيراً عن قراره، وتنحّى جانباً ليُفسح المجال إلى مريض آخر، ولكن من الصين.","english":"After the Russian patient Vladimir Spiridonov agreed to volunteer in the performance of the process and the replacement of his body affected by muscle and nerve dystrophy by a body of a healthy but brain-dead man, he ultimately apologized for his decision and stepped aside to make room for another patient, but from China."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of فَسَحَ (fasaḥa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/fa.su.ħa/","/fa.sa.ħa/","/fas.sa.ħa/","/fasħ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n33826","headword_ar":"فَسُحَ","root":"fsH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (MA, Msb, K, [in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fasaHa","text_ar":"فَسَحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a misprint,]) with damm, (Msb,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"karuma","text_ar":"كَرُمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":",] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fusaAHapN","text_ar":"فُسَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fasaAHapN","text_ar":"فَسَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[for which the former is app. a mistranscription] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fusoHapN","text_ar":"فُسْحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (MA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a place)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, spacious, roomy, wide,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ample;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AfsH","text_ar":"افسح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tfs~H","text_ar":"تفسّح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AnfsH","text_ar":"انفسح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fasaHa lahu","text_ar":"فَسَحَ لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, MA, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fasoHN","text_ar":"فَسْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, Msb, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fusuwHN","text_ar":"فُسُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tfs~H","text_ar":"تفسّح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AfsH","text_ar":"افسح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made room,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ample room, for him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, MA, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Almajolisi","text_ar":"فِى المَجْلِسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, MA, Msb)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the sitting-place,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the assembly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Almajolisi","text_ar":"فِى المَجْلِسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tafas~aHuwA","text_ar":"تَفَسَّحُوا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, *) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tafaA saHuwA","text_ar":"تَفَا سَحُوا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Make ye room,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ample space,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the sitting-place,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the assembly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tawas~aEuwA","text_ar":"تَوَسَّعُوا"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) both of these verbs have nearly the same signification: [each may be rendered, but the latter more properly,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"make ye room,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ample space, one for another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the latter occurs, accord. to the reading of El-Hasan, and the former accord. to that of others, in the Kur lviii. 12. (Fr, TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AifosaHo Ean~iY","text_ar":"اِفْسَحْ عَنِّى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Remove thou, withdraw,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retire to a distance, from me."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ksh and Bd in lviii. 12.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fasoHN","text_ar":"فَسْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fasaHa","text_ar":"فَسَحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] also signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"making wide steps;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fayosaHaY","text_ar":"فَيْسَحَى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AifosaHi AlxuTaY","text_ar":"اِفْسَحِ الخُطَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", said by an Arab of the Desert, of the Benoo-'Okeyl, to one who was sewing for him a water-skin, and mentioned in the T, as heard by its author, meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Make wide the spaces between each two punctures of the needle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"lest the punctures should rend. (L.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fasaHa lahu AlA^amiyru fiY Als~afari","text_ar":"فَسَحَ لَهُ الاَمِيرُ فِى السَّفَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The commander,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"governor, wrote for him a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fasoH","text_ar":"فَسْح"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (K.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","K","L","MA","S","TA","A"]},{"entry_id":"n33827","headword_ar":"فسّح","root":"fsH","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made"},{"kind":"text","text":"a place"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spacious, roomy, wide,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ample."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n33829","headword_ar":"فَسْحٌ","root":"fsH","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A writing like a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawaAz","text_ar":"جَوَاز"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"traveller's pass"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.) [See 1, last sentence.]"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n33830","headword_ar":"فُسُحٌ","root":"fsH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fasiyHN","text_ar":"فَسِيحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}